Actress Toyin Abraham has become the first brand Ambassador for Checkers Custard. Before the official announcement, the movie producer had hinted how she woke up to mail to become the brand ambassador of a brand her family have been using for over three years. She has, however, disclosed the brand on a video posted on her Instagram page with the caption: “Ladies and gentlemen, meet the first and only brand ambassador for the best custard @checkerscustard.   Reactions as Portable adorns suit for first time     PVCs should be substituted for show tickets, says…     I’ve been dreaming of DJ Cuppy- Lord Lamba   “@checkerscustard is not only best custard in Nigeria it is the best in Africa infact the best in the world. They are your go to custard for a premium taste. - Advertisement - “So smooth. It gets you fueled and energized. With them, you enjoy the taste of real custard. “TOYINTITANS, welcome our new family @checkerscustard with massive love and support. Follow them on @checkerscustard and show them love.”